  <title>Automatic Door using Servo Motor </title>
<subsection xml:id="subsec-Introduction-door">
  <title>Introduction</title>
  <p>
    Automatic door is an intelligent system to open and close the door without any human intervention. When an object is in front of the door It will open the door automatically with the help of servo motor. It is also used in shopping malls, offices and so on. Working of automatic door is similar to the previous experiment automatic sanitizer using IR sensor (chapter 3.3). Table 3.1.1, explains requirement of hardware components. Below image displays the automatic door which is used in many places. 
  </p>
  <image source="/images/DOOR.jpg" width="40%"/>
</subsection>
