    In fig 3.1.4, when there is no object detected by the IR sensor the door of the small house remains closed.  When IR sensors==0 the servo motor will remain in the idle position.  
  </p>
  <p>
    In fig 3.1.5, when the IR sensor ==1 detects the object.  The servo motor will rotate 90 degree which can pull the one side of the door to open. 
